snippet.title: Nick Jonas & Priyanka Chopra Open Up About Their Wedding, Amber Heard On 'Aquaman' | PeopleTV
snippet.description:
Newlyweds Nick Jonas and Priyanka Chopra open up about their emotional wedding. Amber Heard shares the message she wants younger girls to take away from ‘Aquaman.’ Ariana Grande asks fans to ‘be gentler’ with Pete Davidson. Kimberly Williams-Paisley joins us live to dish on her new movie ‘The Christmas Chronicles.’ Ryan Reynolds thinks being a dad has ‘made me a better person.’ John Legend dishes on what he thinks about him and Chrissy Teigen being #couplegoals. Dolly Parton reveals that her husband wants to have a threesome with Jennifer Aniston.
